Y by Adventure10, Mango247Calculation Bash Solution\begin{align*} 14641_{99} &= 1 \cdot 99^0 + 4 \cdot 99^1 + 6 \cdot 99^2 + 4 \cdot 99^3 + 1 \cdot 99^4 \\&= 1 + 396 + 6 \cdot 9801 + 4 \cdot 970299 + 96059601 \\&= \boxed {100000000} \end{align*}

Quick Solution\begin{align*} 14641_{99} &= 1 \cdot 99^0 + 4 \cdot 99^1 + 6 \cdot 99^2 + 4 \cdot 99^3 + 1 \cdot 99^4 \\&= (1 + 99)^4 \qquad \text {(Reverse Binomial Theorem)} \\&= 100^4 = (10^2)^4 \\&= 10^8 = \boxed {100000000} \end{align*}

